          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Also, the interior looks nothing like the C8. Gone is the strip of controls, replaced by an even more modern and cleaner layout. Alcantara, Nappa leather, carbon fiber, and aluminum adorn the cabin, making it feel appropriately high end.",
